{"id": 868, "genre": 1001, "title": "你对天气应用有什么期待？", "description": "“天气实在太好了！”“今天实在太（哔——）冷了！”你告诉我这些足够了，我不想在你这交朋友，谢谢。", "record_count": 3100, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183742p6dfgxlnPXEKGJQ4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-03-16T11:17:02Z", "options": [{"id": 59144, "content": "真实可靠", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 486532}, {"id": 61965, "content": "天气级好好做天气，报了了天气你就得保证你报的准确\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 497986}, {"id": 59920, "content": "软件要专业", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 230672}, {"id": 61205, "content": "认真预报，别让我总是更新", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 499266}, {"id": 59418, "content": "幽默的定义是“嘿今天有80%的可能妹子们会穿短裤记得看腿之前带上墨镜”而不是“嘿你的联系人王建国也使用这个软件要不要跟他加个好友聊聊天”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 521093}, {"id": 61215, "content": "功能齐全，不要广告。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532199}, {"id": 58918, "content": "不下雨就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 465764}, {"id": 58920, "content": "实时提醒做好就够了", "image": null, "praise_count": 103, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172035}, {"id": 58922, "content": "自动调节闹钟，下雨提醒早出门。", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272649}, {"id": 61738, "content": "准确的预测", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535072}, {"id": 61739, "content": "准确的预测", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535072}, {"id": 58925, "content": "界面简洁 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 351, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403246}, {"id": 59182, "content": "自从有了新闻，app越来越大我就直接扔了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 512092}, {"id": 58927, "content": "平常不管用 极端天气请通知我！", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518357}, {"id": 58928, "content": "简洁只报天气，软件尽量小", "image": null, "praise_count": 520, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 512849}, {"id": 58929, "content": "希望能够有实时实况的奖赏 让更多的人实时发表天气状态（这样方便更多人 因为虽然有的时候在同一个城市，到了某个地方天气要么冷了要么热了）", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506043}, {"id": 58930, "content": "好好报天气。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518377}, {"id": 58931, "content": "2小时内精准天气预报", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436005}, {"id": 58932, "content": "“准”是唯一要求", "image": null, "praise_count": 442, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313098}, {"id": 59956, "content": "界面简洁，进阶信息放在下一级界面", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 524783}, {"id": 58933, "content": "不需要打開app，在小插件上以彈窗形式顯示具體內容", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400195}, {"id": 59189, "content": "语音提示我明天天气，因为我会忘记看天气", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519867}, {"id": 59190, "content": "推荐MyWeather。几乎完美的APP。", "image": "img/option/option/201606061449224VlG6QLPioRMx9pA.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453378}, {"id": 58936, "content": "天气预报准就行，别名人语音了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 499302}, {"id": 58937, "content": "预报就预报，别搞那么多乱七八糟的跳转，推送", "image": null, "praise_count": 116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 510080}, {"id": 58938, "content": "我就想知道露大腿妹子的出现几率。", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 501373}, {"id": 58939, "content": "准", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 513996}, {"id": 58940, "content": "最好预报人以身示范衣服穿着厚度", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 474416}, {"id": 58941, "content": "该穿什么衣服/头发容易油吗/带多大的伞/最适合天气的刷牙洗脸歌推荐/交通", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 512482}, {"id": 58943, "content": "开启弹幕吐槽模式", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 355122}, {"id": 58944, "content": "能把天气预报设置成闹钟吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 58179, "content": "好好预报，别搞社交。 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 851, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 58947, "content": "及时提醒功能 不想再买地铁口的?了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107785}, {"id": 58181, "content": "最好可以有详细的推荐穿多少衣服的功能，那种“今天建议穿外套”这样含糊的穿衣建议好像没啥用", "image": null, "praise_count": 178, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 59717, "content": "麻烦考虑现实好么不是气温高就可以穿少的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 523116}, {"id": 58950, "content": "我把有关简洁的都点了一遍赞，让墨迹过来看看！或者有什么简洁的天气应用推荐的吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 430767}, {"id": 58183, "content": "自动连通健身APP，PM2.5太高就憋叫我出门跑步了", "image": null, "praise_count": 93, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 58951, "content": "做的可爱点，提示啥时候应该晒东西，提示可以出行游玩的推荐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 331384}, {"id": 58184, "content": "雅虎天气的图片质量不要下滑啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 58952, "content": "有街景的动图显示就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 60488, "content": "准确才是最重要的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527712}, {"id": 58185, "content": "用天气生成吐槽，就好像你的朋友会说的：天气实在太好了，或者今天实在太（哔——）冷了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 58953, "content": "让我看看昨天天气温度好么？不然温度只是数字，没有太大参考价值。ps，补日记时缺天气这项很心酸", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460062}, {"id": 58954, "content": "准点\n不要外面大太阳还告我阴天", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 58957, "content": "不用给我预测未来20天 明天的能预测的靠谱一点的就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 459807}, {"id": 58958, "content": "好好播报天气，别弄没用的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276118}, {"id": 58959, "content": "告诉我何时台风停学", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517933}, {"id": 59217, "content": "准就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 446327}, {"id": 58963, "content": "无广告，界面简洁", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311495}, {"id": 60755, "content": "没有天气应用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528992}]}